This is not to brag, actually I'm the first one to admit I'm not some god tier trader or a giga brain and that I've been lucky and I'm very grateful for it
I still think there's a few points of advice that might be helpful to someone

Azima 🛸: After losses, taxes & cashing out some funds for irl purposes. I am restarting my crypto journey with 10% of my ath nw. Very grateful when looking back at where I was 2-3 years ago.
Time to grind again..
